column5: I was sent a message that Brookside had 100% hatched on Friday & the rest of the schools are reporting they have all started to hatch, the students are very excited & asking lots of question, Aquarium temperatures are going up from 45 degrees to 50 degrees to help them grow quicker. Tight Lines SBK  LHFC School Hatchery Blog
Great project!,good to see the interest in the kids.
